WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:05.829
<i>[eerie music]</i>

00:05.923 --> 00:09.416
<i>(narrator) YOU UNLOCK THIS DOOR
WITH THE KEY OF IMAGINATION.</i>

00:09.510 --> 00:11.842
<i>BEYOND IT
IS ANOTHER DIMENSION--</i>

00:11.887 --> 00:13.343
<i>A DIMENSION OF SOUND,</i>

00:13.388 --> 00:14.890
<i>[glass shattering]</i>

00:14.973 --> 00:16.350
<i>A DIMENSION OF SIGHT,</i>

00:16.391 --> 00:18.382
<i>A DIMENSION OF MIND.</i>

00:18.477 --> 00:21.686
<i>YOU'RE MOVING INTO A LAND
OF BOTH SHADOW AND SUBSTANCE,</i>

00:21.772 --> 00:23.638
<i>OF THINGS AND IDEAS.</i>

00:23.732 --> 00:26.645
<i>YOU'VE JUST CROSSED OVER
INTO THE TWILIGHT ZONE.</i>

00:39.248 --> 00:41.535
CHARLIE?

00:41.625 --> 00:45.084
GO BACK TO SLEEP,
ELLA, IT'S EARLY.

00:45.170 --> 00:46.547
WHAT TIME IS IT?

00:48.632 --> 00:49.872
MY WATCH STOPPED.

00:49.967 --> 00:51.549
IT'S PITCH BLACK OUT.

00:51.593 --> 00:54.210
IT MUST BE 3:00 OR
4:00 IN THE MORNING.

00:54.304 --> 00:56.591
LOOK HOW BLACK
IT IS OUT THERE.

00:56.682 --> 00:58.889
IT'S THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT.

00:58.934 --> 01:01.801
OH, I THINK YOU'RE
CRAZY TO GET UP NOW.

01:01.895 --> 01:03.101
WHAT'S SO SPECIAL

01:03.188 --> 01:05.099
ABOUT HANGING
A LITTLE...

01:05.190 --> 01:07.397
GO BACK
TO SLEEP, ELLA!

01:07.484 --> 01:09.395
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU?

01:09.444 --> 01:12.311
YOU'LL HAVE ALL
THAT EXCITEMENT TODAY.

01:12.406 --> 01:14.898
YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT NEEDS THE SLEEP.

01:14.992 --> 01:17.950
BRING HIS BREAKFAST
OVER ABOUT 8:30.

01:18.036 --> 01:23.281
WHAT TIME THEY
STRING HIM UP?

01:23.375 --> 01:24.911
WELL, YOU KNOW
WHAT I MEAN.

01:25.002 --> 01:26.584
WHAT TIME DOES
HE GET HUNG?

01:26.670 --> 01:29.458
<i>HE GETS
EXECUTED</i> AT 9:30.

01:29.548 --> 01:31.084
AND I HOPE
THE WHOLE TOWN

01:31.174 --> 01:32.756
DOESN'T TURN OUT.

01:32.843 --> 01:34.800
WHEN I SEE A BUNCH OF
COLDBLOODED GAWKERS

01:34.886 --> 01:37.344
GETTING THEIR JOLLIES
FROM SEEING A MAN DIE,

01:37.431 --> 01:40.594
I JUST...

01:40.684 --> 01:44.348
JUST BRING HIS BREAKFAST
OVER AT 8:30.

01:44.438 --> 01:46.020
OH, CHARLIE?

01:46.106 --> 01:48.268
HOW DOES HE
LIKE HIS EGGS?

01:48.358 --> 01:49.860
EDIBLE.

01:49.943 --> 01:51.729
THEY'RE THE LAST ONES
HE'S GOING TO EAT

01:51.820 --> 01:55.438
SO MAKE THEM EDIBLE.

01:55.532 --> 02:02.245
[clock chiming]

02:10.464 --> 02:12.956
I DON'T GET IT.

02:13.050 --> 02:16.418
WHAT DON'T YOU
GET, DEPUTY?

02:16.511 --> 02:18.718
SHERIFF, IT'S 7:30
IN THE MORNING,

02:18.805 --> 02:20.796
AND IT'S PITCH
BLACK OUTSIDE.

02:20.891 --> 02:23.724
I'VE NEVER SEEN
IT ANY BLACKER,

02:23.810 --> 02:26.472
BUT IT'S 7:30
IN THE MORNING.

02:26.563 --> 02:27.769
NOW, WHAT'S
GOING ON?

02:46.500 --> 02:49.162
I DON'T KNOW, DEPUTY.

02:49.252 --> 02:53.587
IT'S 7:30 IN THE MORNING
AND IT'S PITCH BLACK OUTSIDE.

02:53.674 --> 02:56.336
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH...

02:56.426 --> 02:58.167
I DON'T KNOW WHY.

02:58.261 --> 03:00.844
I DON'T KNOW WHY AT ALL.

03:00.931 --> 03:03.423
<i>(narrator)
SHERIFF CHARLIE KOCH</i>

03:03.517 --> 03:05.849
<i>ON THE MORNING
OF AN EXECUTION.</i>

03:05.936 --> 03:09.520
<i>AS A MATTER OF FACT,
IT'S 7:30 IN THE MORNING.</i>

03:09.564 --> 03:12.522
LOGIC AND NATURAL LAVVS
DICTATE THAT AT THIS HOUR

03:12.609 --> 03:14.270
THERE SHOULD BE DAYLIGHT.

03:14.361 --> 03:16.602
IT IS A SIMPLE RULE
OF PHYSICAL SCIENCE

03:16.697 --> 03:19.610
THAT THE SUN SHOULD RISE
AT A CERTAIN MOMENT

03:19.700 --> 03:21.361
AND SUPERSEDE THE DARKNESS.

03:21.451 --> 03:24.113
BUT AT THIS GIVEN MOMENT
SHERIFF CHARLIE KOCH,

03:24.204 --> 03:27.447
A DEPUTY NAMED PIERCE,
A CONDEMNED MAN NAMED JAGGER,

03:27.541 --> 03:29.532
AND A SMALL,
INCONSEQUENTIAL VILLAGE

03:29.626 --> 03:33.119
WILL SHORTLY FIND OUT THAT
THERE ARE CAUSES AND EFFECTS

03:33.213 --> 03:34.874
THAT HAVE NO PRECEDENT.

03:34.965 --> 03:37.252
SUCH IS USUALLY THE CASE
IN THE TWILIGHT ZONE.

04:01.241 --> 04:02.481
HOW ABOUT THAT?

04:02.576 --> 04:03.987
YOU SEE IT OUTSIDE?

04:04.077 --> 04:05.909
YOU BETTER
RUN AN EXTRA

04:05.996 --> 04:07.907
IN THAT PAPER
OF YOURS.

04:07.998 --> 04:09.739
I'VE BEEN ANSWERING
THE PHONE

04:09.833 --> 04:11.665
SINCE 6:00 THIS MORNING.

04:11.752 --> 04:14.995
ONE FELLOW CALLED, SAID THE
ELECTRICITY HAD GONE OFF--

04:15.088 --> 04:17.079
IT WAS TOMORROW NIGHT.

04:17.173 --> 04:19.211
ANOTHER GODLY WOMAN,

04:19.301 --> 04:23.010
VVHO PROFESSES TO READ HER GOOD
BOOK VVITH ADMIRABLE REGULARITY,

04:23.096 --> 04:25.337
TELLS ME IT'S
THE END OF THE WORLD

04:25.432 --> 04:29.596
AND SHE CAN QUOTE THE CHAPTER AND
VERSE TO SUPPORT HER THESIS.

04:29.686 --> 04:31.848
NOW, YOU'RE WELL-VERSED
IN ALL THINGS

04:31.938 --> 04:34.430
REGARDING LAW AND
ORDER, SHERIFF KOCH.

04:34.524 --> 04:36.265
WHAT'S YOUR THESIS?

04:36.359 --> 04:37.861
IT'S A QUARTER TO EIGHT.

04:37.944 --> 04:39.651
IT'S A QUARTER TO EIGHT
IN THE MORNING

04:39.738 --> 04:41.445
AND IT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE.

04:41.531 --> 04:43.784
DAYLIGHT SHOULD HAVE
COME TWO HOURS AGO.

04:43.867 --> 04:45.858
WELL, IN BETWEEN
REASSURING PEOPLE

04:45.952 --> 04:48.535
THAT THIS VVAS NOT AN
INTERPLANETARY INVASION,

04:48.622 --> 04:50.112
NOR THE END
OF THE WORLD,

04:50.207 --> 04:52.790
I PLACED A CALL TO
THE STATE CAPITAL.

04:52.876 --> 04:54.458
IS IT BLACK THERE?

04:54.544 --> 04:56.706
IT APPEARS THAT
ACROSS THE FACE

04:56.797 --> 04:58.379
OF THE ENTIRE EARTH

04:58.465 --> 05:00.672
WE ARE THE ONLY ONES
GROPING IN DARKNESS.

05:00.759 --> 05:02.966
SO IT SEEMS
THE PHENOMENON

05:03.053 --> 05:04.543
IS QUITE LOCALIZED

05:04.638 --> 05:07.801
AND WE'LL JUST HAVE
TO SEEK ELSEWHERE

05:07.891 --> 05:10.633
FOR COMPANY TO
SHARE OUR MISERY.

05:10.685 --> 05:12.813
HAVE YOU SEEN
JAGGER THIS MORNING?

05:12.896 --> 05:14.478
I SEEN HIM.

05:14.564 --> 05:16.896
I BROUGHT HIM IN
A CUP OF COFFEE.

05:16.983 --> 05:21.398
I ALSO REMINDED HIM ABOUT
VVHAT DAY IT VVAS.

05:21.488 --> 05:24.321
I'LL BET YOU DID.

05:24.407 --> 05:27.320
HOVV DID YOU OCCUPY
YOURSELF AS A LAD, DEPUTY?

05:27.410 --> 05:28.787
TORTURING SMALL ANIMALS

05:28.870 --> 05:30.986
OR JUST PULLING
WINGS OFF FLIES?

05:31.081 --> 05:33.573
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
BY THAT, MR. COLBEY?

05:33.667 --> 05:35.328
NOTHING.

05:35.418 --> 05:37.580
NOTHING AT ALL.

05:37.671 --> 05:39.708
CAN I TALK TO JAGGER?

05:39.798 --> 05:41.664
GO RIGHT ON IN.

05:41.716 --> 05:43.707
AS A POINT OF
INTEREST, SHERIFF,

05:43.802 --> 05:45.918
IS JAGGER INNOCENT?

05:46.012 --> 05:48.925
THAT IS A MATTER FOR
A JURY, PUBLIC OPINION AND GOD,

05:49.015 --> 05:51.677
AND THAT, THANK THE LORD,
HAS NOTHING TO DO WITH ME.

05:51.768 --> 05:55.352
SO LET US ALL PRAISE GOD FOR
THE MORNING'S IMPARTIALITY.

05:55.438 --> 05:59.432
AND FOR JUSTICE BEING
SERVED DELUXE STYLE.

05:59.526 --> 06:00.857
<i>DEPUTY...</i>

06:00.944 --> 06:03.686
WHY DON'T YOU
SHUT YOUR MOUTH.

06:03.780 --> 06:05.282
I GOT A RIGHT
TO AN OPINION.

06:05.365 --> 06:07.356
INDEED YOU
HAVE, DEPUTY.

06:07.450 --> 06:08.986
INDEED YOU HAVE.

06:09.077 --> 06:12.445
BUT THERE'S JUST A FEW
DISTURBING FACETS

06:12.539 --> 06:13.870
ABOUT THIS CASE.

06:13.957 --> 06:15.447
ONE...

06:15.542 --> 06:17.624
THE MURDERED MAN
WAS NOT A DECENT MAN.

06:17.711 --> 06:20.794
HE WAS A CROSS-BURNING,
PSYCHOPATHIC BULLY

06:20.881 --> 06:22.963
WHO ATTACKED
THE MAN IN THERE.

06:23.049 --> 06:26.132
AND TVVO, DEPUTY PIERCE
HERE SAVV IT HAPPEN

06:26.219 --> 06:28.130
AND THEN PERJURED HIMSELF.

06:28.221 --> 06:30.462
NOW, WAIT A MINUTE!

06:30.557 --> 06:32.798
PERJURED IS
THE WORD, DEPUTY.

06:32.893 --> 06:35.305
NOW, YOU SAID
JAGGER SHOT HIM

06:35.395 --> 06:37.227
FROM ACROSS THE ROOM.

06:37.314 --> 06:38.645
NO SUCH THING.

06:44.779 --> 06:47.567
THE MURDERED MAN HAD
POWDER BURNS ALL OVER HIM.

06:47.657 --> 06:49.648
THIS MIGHT NOT HAVE
PROVEN SELF-DEFENSE

06:49.743 --> 06:52.735
BUT IT WOULD'VE POINTED
TO IT AND MAYBE HELPED IT.

06:52.829 --> 06:55.992
AND YOU, SHERIFF KOCH,
YOU SAW THE BODY.

06:56.082 --> 06:57.823
BUT I DIDN'T HEAR
ANY COMMENTS

06:57.918 --> 06:59.204
ON THOSE
POWDER BURNS

06:59.294 --> 07:01.126
WHEN YOU GAVE
YOUR TESTIMONY.

07:01.212 --> 07:04.750
AND YOUR COURAGEOUS EDITOR
HERE IN COVERING THE TRIAL

07:04.841 --> 07:08.755
DIDN'T SEE FIT TO INCLUDE
THIS INSIGNIFICANT ADDENDUM

07:08.845 --> 07:13.089
THOUGH HE ALSO KNEVV AT THE TIME
HE VVAS BEING VERY SELECTIVE

07:13.183 --> 07:17.677
ABOUT VVHAT TRUTHS HE VVAS WRITING
ABOUT, VVHAT TRUTHS HE VVASN'T.

07:17.771 --> 07:19.353
YOU'RE RIGHT, DEPUTY.

07:19.439 --> 07:21.350
<i>JUSTICE IS
BEING SERVED...</i>

07:21.441 --> 07:24.183
ON A PLATTER WITH
ITS TONGUE CUT OUT

07:24.277 --> 07:28.316
JUST LIKE THE CARCASS
OF ANY DEAD ANIMAL.

07:37.874 --> 07:43.210
LET ME KNOW WHEN
YOU'RE READY.

07:43.296 --> 07:45.458
IT'S PITCH BLACK OUTSIDE.

07:45.548 --> 07:47.710
ALMOST 8:00
IN THE MORNING.

07:47.801 --> 07:49.838
NOT A SPECK
OF DAYLIGHT.

07:49.928 --> 07:52.386
THIS PLACE DOESN'T
HAVE ANY WINDOWS

07:52.472 --> 07:54.304
SO IT COULD
BE CHRISTMAS EVE

07:54.391 --> 07:55.847
OR THE FOURTH OF JULY

07:55.934 --> 07:58.301
AND I WOULD NOT KNOW
THE DIFFERENCE.

07:58.395 --> 08:01.729
YOU GOT ANY RELIGIOUS
AFFILIATION, JAGGER?

08:01.815 --> 08:03.397
NONE.

08:03.483 --> 08:05.394
ANYONE YOU WANT TO SEE?

08:05.485 --> 08:07.067
NOBODY.

08:07.153 --> 08:10.987
ANYTHING TO SAY?

08:11.074 --> 08:13.816
NOTHING.

08:13.910 --> 08:16.322
NO PRIEST, NO FRIENDS,
NO COMMENT.

08:16.413 --> 08:18.745
JUST WHAT HAVE
YOU GOT, JAGGER?

08:18.832 --> 08:20.414
I GOT THE BLUES, MR. COLBEY!

08:20.500 --> 08:22.161
I GOT THE BLUES.

08:22.252 --> 08:24.334
I'M JUST ABOUT AN HOUR
AVVAY FROM A HANGING

08:24.421 --> 08:26.003
AND I'VE BEEN LYING THERE

08:26.089 --> 08:27.875
AND I HAVE BEEN THINKING
THAT I WOULD LIKE

08:27.966 --> 08:32.506
TO RIP THESE BARS APART
AND GET OUT OF HERE.

08:32.595 --> 08:35.428
OR I'D LIKE TO SAVE
EVERYBODY ELSE THE TROUBLE

08:35.515 --> 08:38.758
AND HANG MYSELF
RIGHT HERE.

08:38.852 --> 08:40.683
BUT I DON'T HAVE
THE STRENGTH FOR ONE

08:40.770 --> 08:42.852
OR THE GUTS
FOR THE OTHER

08:42.897 --> 08:48.358
SO I'M JUST LYING THERE,
AND I AM JUST WAITING.

08:48.445 --> 08:52.188
VVELL, IN THAT CASE, VVOULD
YOU CARE TO MAKE A STATEMENT

08:52.282 --> 08:54.239
ABOUT GUILT
OR INNOCENCE?

08:54.325 --> 08:57.454
GUILT OR INNOCENCE, AND YOU
VVANT ME TO MAKE A STATEMENT?

08:57.537 --> 08:59.198
<i>I'D APPRECIATE ONE.</i>

08:59.289 --> 09:01.200
I DON'T THINK ANYBODY
SHOULD LEAVE THIS EARTH

09:01.291 --> 09:04.374
VVITHOUT MAKING A
COMMENT-YOU, ME, ANYBODY.

09:04.461 --> 09:06.543
WELL, THAT'S A REASONABLE
REQUEST, MR. COLBEY.

09:06.629 --> 09:09.212
CONSIDERING THE FACT THAT
YOU'RE NOT LEAVING THIS MORNING

09:09.299 --> 09:10.289
IT'S REASONABLE.

09:12.886 --> 09:15.469
I'M GUILTY, MR. COLBEY.

09:15.555 --> 09:18.798
THAT TAKE YOU
OFF THE HOOK?

09:18.892 --> 09:21.224
AND THAT'S SUPPOSED
TO MEAN WHAT?

09:21.311 --> 09:22.893
THAT'S SUPPOSED
TO MEAN

09:22.979 --> 09:24.640
YOU'RE ON THE
POPULAR SIDE.

09:24.731 --> 09:26.813
THERE ARE GOOD GUYS
AND BAD GUYS--

09:26.900 --> 09:28.311
THAT'S THE NATURE OF MAN.

09:28.401 --> 09:30.233
WELL, I'M WORSE
THAN A BAD GUY.

09:30.320 --> 09:32.152
I'M A TOWN KOOK,
I'M A NEUROTIC.

09:32.238 --> 09:34.491
I'M THE ONE VVITH THE
CAUSES AND THE BANNERS.

09:34.574 --> 09:37.532
I'M THE VILLAGE IDIOT VVHO TRIES
TO BE HIS BROTHER'S KEEPER.

09:48.171 --> 09:50.333
DO YOU UNDERSTAND,
MR. COLBEY?

09:50.423 --> 09:53.916
THE MAN I KILLED WAS
THE WHITE KNIGHT.

09:53.968 --> 09:56.585
<i>HE DID WHAT HIS OTHER
PALS IN THIS TOWN</i>

09:56.679 --> 09:59.091
<i>WANTED TO DO AND
DIDN'T HAVE THE GUTS.</i>

09:59.182 --> 10:02.015
<i>HE WAS THE CROSS BURNER,
THE BOMB THROWER.</i>

10:02.102 --> 10:08.018
<i>HE</i> HANDLED THE VVHIPPING OF
SOME POOR, SCARED COLORED GUY.

10:08.108 --> 10:11.442
OH...

10:11.528 --> 10:13.110
THE MAN YOU KILLED
WAS NO SAINT

10:13.196 --> 10:15.028
BUT WE DON'T DISPENSE
LIFE OR DEATH

10:15.115 --> 10:16.947
JUST BECAUSE SOMEBODY
OFFENDS US.

10:16.991 --> 10:19.483
THAT'S THE DISTINCTION
BETWEEN MEN AND ANIMALS.

10:19.577 --> 10:21.955
OH, WELL, THAT'S
VERY WELL SAID.

10:22.038 --> 10:24.370
THAT'S VERY WELL SAID,
MR. COLBEY.

10:24.457 --> 10:25.959
<i>YOU TELL THAT
TO THE MAN</i>

10:26.042 --> 10:27.624
<i>WHO'S GONNA
FIX MY ROPE.</i>

10:27.710 --> 10:30.122
YOU TELL IT TO THE SHERIFF
AND HIS DEPUTY

10:30.213 --> 10:33.205
TO THE TOVVNSPEOPLE VVHO
ARE GOING TO STAND AROUND

10:33.299 --> 10:36.212
<i>AND WATCH MY EYES BULGE
OUT AND ENJOY MY AGONY.</i>

10:36.302 --> 10:39.135
YOU TELL THEM.

10:39.222 --> 10:41.054
<i>YOU TELL THEM
ABOUT THE DIFFERENCE</i>

10:41.141 --> 10:42.677
<i>BETWEEN MEN
AND ANIMALS.</i>

10:42.767 --> 10:44.633
BUT YOU BETTER BE READY
TO DRAW PICTURES

10:44.686 --> 10:47.178
BECAUSE THIS LANGUAGE
THEY JUST DON'T DIG!

10:51.317 --> 10:56.812
[clock chiming]

10:56.906 --> 11:01.571
[chiming continues]

11:19.053 --> 11:20.305
<i>[radio news playing]</i>

11:20.388 --> 11:22.220
(man)
9:00 IN THE MORNING.

11:22.307 --> 11:23.843
BUT WHY IS IT SO DARK?

11:23.892 --> 11:25.803
IS IT
AN ECLIPSE?

11:25.894 --> 11:27.510
CAN'T BE.

11:27.604 --> 11:29.470
I'M LISTENING
TO THE RADIO.

11:29.564 --> 11:30.804
AIN'T NO ECLIPSE.

11:30.899 --> 11:32.060
IT'S WEIRD.

11:32.150 --> 11:34.482
IT'S JUST
PLAIN WEIRD.

11:34.569 --> 11:37.152
<i>(male announcer) BUT SCIENTISTS
CAN OFFER NO EXPLANATION</i>

11:37.238 --> 11:39.445
<i>FOR THE STRANGE
PHENOMENON OF DARKNESS</i>

11:39.532 --> 11:41.569
<i>THAT HAS SUDDENLY
AND INEXPLICABLY</i>

11:41.659 --> 11:44.447
<i>COVERED THE REMOTE LITTLE
MIDWESTERN VILLAGE.</i>

11:44.537 --> 11:47.154
<i>IT IS NOW 9:00 A.M.
EASTERN STANDARD TIME</i>

11:47.248 --> 11:50.286
<i>BUT LAST REPORTS INDICATE
DARKNESS THERE IS TOTAL.</i>

11:50.376 --> 11:56.588
<i>THERE IS NO REMOTE HINT
OF ANY KIND OF DAYLIGHT.</i>

11:56.674 --> 11:59.837
LOOKS PRETTY GOOD.

11:59.928 --> 12:04.422
THAT OUGHT TO
TEND TO HIM.

12:04.515 --> 12:09.510
BUT WHO'S GONNA
TEND TO US?

12:09.604 --> 12:14.269
WHO OR WHAT IS
GONNA TEND TO US?

12:28.164 --> 12:31.077
<i>(Colbey)
TEN MORE MINUTES.</i>

12:31.167 --> 12:32.828
<i>YOU, UH,
GOING TO GO THROUGH</i>

12:32.919 --> 12:34.159
WITH THIS, SHERIFF?

12:34.254 --> 12:35.870
WHY NOT?

12:35.964 --> 12:39.628
THE LAW SAYS MAY 25,
AT 9:30 IN THE MORNING.

12:39.717 --> 12:41.299
WELL, IT'S MAY 25,

12:41.386 --> 12:44.174
AND IT'LL BE 9:30
IN THE MORNING.

12:44.264 --> 12:46.631
QUITE APART FROM
THE FACT, MR. PIERCE,

12:46.724 --> 12:49.182
THAT YOU'RE NOT THE
MOST SENSITIVE OF MEN,

12:49.269 --> 12:50.680
DID IT EVER OCCUR TO YOU

12:50.770 --> 12:52.932
THERE'S SOMETHING
ODD GOING ON HERE

12:53.022 --> 12:55.810
AND WE BETTER DISPENSE
WITH BUSINESS AS USUAL

12:55.900 --> 12:58.608
UNTIL WE FIND OUT
EXACTLY WHAT IS GOING ON?

12:58.653 --> 13:00.439
YOU KNOW SOMETHING?

13:00.530 --> 13:03.522
I TAKE AN AWFUL LOT
OF DIRT FROM YOU.

13:03.616 --> 13:06.199
AND JUST WHO
ARE YOU, ANYWAY?

13:06.286 --> 13:09.278
A LITTLE-SHOT EDITOR OF
A CRUMMY LITTLE PAPER.

13:09.372 --> 13:11.613
THAT'S RIGHT,
A CRUMMY LITTLE PAPER

13:11.708 --> 13:14.120
THAT CRAWLS ALONG ON
ITS HANDS AND KNEES

13:14.210 --> 13:16.076
FROM ONE EDITION
TO THE OTHER.

13:16.170 --> 13:18.832
YOU GOT MORE CREDITORS
THAN YOU GOT READERS.

13:18.923 --> 13:20.379
THAT'LL DO
IT, PIERCE.

13:20.466 --> 13:22.503
NO, THAT WON'T DO IT
BY A LONG SHOT!

13:22.593 --> 13:24.630
NOW, MAYBE YOU
FEEL LIKE TURNING

13:24.721 --> 13:26.086
YOUR CHEEK
TO THIS CRUMB

13:26.180 --> 13:27.887
BUT THERE AIN'T
NO RULE BOOK

13:27.974 --> 13:29.385
THAT SAYS I GOT TO.

13:29.475 --> 13:31.557
<i>HE SAYS
IPERJURED MYSELF;</i>

13:31.644 --> 13:33.510
<i>SAYS I LIED.</i>

13:33.604 --> 13:35.595
AND BOY, HE WASN'T
THROWING NO BOUQUETS

13:35.690 --> 13:36.930
AT YOU, NEITHER.

13:37.025 --> 13:39.562
MAYBE I DON'T
DESERVE ANY.

13:39.652 --> 13:41.734
YOU WERE RIGHT,
YOU KNOW.

13:41.821 --> 13:44.313
I SAW THE VICTIM.

13:44.407 --> 13:47.115
HE DID HAVE
POWDER BURNS.

13:47.201 --> 13:50.193
<i>BUT WHEN A COMMVYTEE OF
TOWNSPEOPLE CAME TO ME</i>

13:50.288 --> 13:52.279
AND SAID THERE'D
BE NO AUTOPSY,

