TO SAY.

16:49.300 --> 16:50.586
THEN LET'S GO.

16:50.676 --> 16:51.837
LET'S GET ON
WITH IT!

16:51.928 --> 16:53.669
(crowd)
YEAH!

16:53.721 --> 16:54.927
