ANY WORDS, REVEREND.

17:21.457 --> 17:24.369
NO QUOTATIONS IN
OR OUT OF THE BIBLE.

17:24.417 --> 17:26.250
COME ON, LET'S GET IT
OVER WITH!

17:26.337 --> 17:27.953
(crowd)
YEAH!

17:28.047 --> 17:29.754
PATIENCE.

17:29.840 --> 17:31.376
PATIENCE!

17:31.467 --> 17:33.208
I PROMISE YOU, I VVILL
