17:53.281 --> 17:54.487
YEAH!

17:54.574 --> 17:56.030
YEAH, YEAH!

17:56.117 --> 17:57.699
[jeering]

17:57.785 --> 17:58.650
YEAH!

17:58.744 --> 18:00.826
YEAH, YEAH!

18:00.913 --> 18:02.950
[crowd falls silent]

18:21.100 --> 18:23.307
DON'T RETURN
THEIR HATE.

18:23.394 --> 18:24.850
DON'T DISHONOR YOURSELF.

18:24.937 --> 18:26.678
WHY DON'T YOU
GET OUT OF HERE.

18:26.772 --> 18:28.354
I GOT TOO MUCH
HATE IN ME

18:28.441 --> 18:30.648
TO KEEP PLUGGED
UP ANYMORE.

18:30.735 --> 18:33.944
WHEN HE CAME
AT YOU, JAGGER...

18:34.030 --> 18:36.522
DID IT FEEL GOOD
TO YOU THEN?

18:36.616 --> 18:38.357
WHAT DIFFERENCE?

18:38.451 --> 18:41.239
WHEN YOU AIMED THAT GUN
AT HIS HEAD,

18:41.329 --> 18:43.036
THAT WASN'T SUCH
A BAD MOMENT, WAS IT?

18:43.122 --> 18:45.363
GOOD, BAD, WHO CARES?

18:45.458 --> 18:48.450
WHEN YOU KILLED HIM,
JAGGER,

18:48.502 --> 18:51.494
WHEN YOU BLEW
HIS HEAD OFF,

18:51.589 --> 18:55.674
<i>THERE WERE NO REGRETS
THEN, WERE THERE'?</i>

18:55.760 --> 18:58.627
