21:33.292 --> 21:34.794
THERE'S JUST TOO MUCH.

21:34.877 --> 21:37.585
<i>AND SO WE HAD
TO VOMIT IT OUT.</i>

21:37.671 --> 21:40.538
<i>AND NOW IT'S COMING
